    <section>
        <h2 class="section_heading">About Sunlit Flavours</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Sunlit Flavours, an academic project designed by me, <strong>Jayant Verma</strong>, as a part of my MCA final semester requirements. This website serves as a demonstration of a comprehensive food ordering platform, showcasing my skills and dedication to building a functional, user-friendly web application.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="section_heading">What is Sunlit Flavours?</h2>
        <p>Sunlit Flavours is a simulated online platform that presents a seamless experience of browsing through a diverse food menu, managing a cart, and initiating an order process. The goal was to develop a project that not only fulfills academic criteria but also highlights a practical understanding of building user-centric web applications.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="section_heading">Features of Sunlit Flavours:</h2>
        <table class="table table-striped">
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Menu Display:</strong></td>
                <td>An engaging page that showcases various dishes, each accompanied by descriptions and images.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Cart Functionality:</strong></td>
                <td>Users can add items to their cart, adjust quantities, and view an updated summary of their selections.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Order Summary:</strong></td>
                <td>A clear breakdown of items added to the cart, ensuring a smooth transition to placing an order.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Contact Section:</strong></td>
                <td>A straightforward way for visitors to connect or learn more about the website.</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="section_heading">Acknowledgements</h2>
        <p>This project was developed through consistent self-learning, research, and the use of official documentation for technologies and frameworks involved. Alongside my own dedication, various reputable online resources played a supportive role in clarifying complex issues and enhancing my understanding of web development concepts.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="section_heading">Potential for the Future</h2>
        <p>While currently built to demonstrate the core functionalities of an online food ordering system, Sunlit Flavours holds the potential to evolve into a complete e-commerce simulation site, offering more dynamic features and an even more immersive experience.</p>
        <p>Thank you for visiting Sunlit Flavours. Your interest and feedback are valued as I continue to learn and grow as a developer.</p>
    </section>
